From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: pai-nix <pai-nix@localhost>
Date: Sun, 3 May 2026 15:05:00 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 9/9] Fix remaining mixed-case path bugs (TOOLS, ALGORITHM)

Upstream issue: danielmiessler/Personal_AI_Infrastructure#1146

Patch 0006 fixed all "Pulse" mixed-case path-construction sites in
the Pulse subsystem (15 sites, 11 files). A wider audit reveals 4
additional sites OUTSIDE Pulse using mixed-case names for canonical
ALL-CAPS directories (PAI/ALGORITHM/, PAI/TOOLS/). On Linux's
case-sensitive filesystem these resolve to non-existent paths; on
macOS HFS+/APFS the bug is invisible.

Sites fixed:

  PAI/PULSE/modules/wiki.ts                         :44
    join(PAI_DIR, "Algorithm")  →  join(PAI_DIR, "ALGORITHM")
    The wiki module reads ~/.claude/PAI/Algorithm/ — non-existent
    on Linux. /api/wiki/algorithm endpoint returns nothing even
    though ~/.claude/PAI/ALGORITHM/v6.3.0.md exists.

  PAI/PAI-Install/engine/actions.ts                 :~1530 (post-0008)
    `alias pai='bun ${join(paiDir, "PAI", "Tools", "pai.ts")}'`
    The installer writes a .zshrc/.bashrc alias pointing to
    ~/.claude/PAI/Tools/pai.ts — non-existent on Linux.
    Cited verbatim in #1146 reproduction transcript. NixOS gates
    this branch via PAI_NIX_INSTALL=1 (patch 0005), but the
    patched binary should still emit the correct alias for non-Nix
    Linux users.

  PAI/TOOLS/pai.ts                                  :34
    join(homedir(), ".claude", "PAI", "Tools", "Banner.ts")
    The pai REPL fails to load its banner script on Linux.

  PAI/TOOLS/MemoryRetriever.ts                      :286
    path.join(PAI_DIR, "Tools", "Inference.ts")
    MemoryRetriever can't find Inference.ts on Linux; the inference
    fallback path silently bails.

Sites considered but NOT changed (correctness-preserving):

  PAI/PAI-Install/engine/actions.ts:1405
    join(skillsDir, s.name, "Tools")
    skills/<name>/Tools/ is the canonical mixed-case path. Upstream
    tarball ships .claude/skills/Aphorisms/Tools/, not /TOOLS/.

  PAI/PULSE/modules/wiki.ts:184  group: "Algorithm"
  PAI/PULSE/modules/wiki.ts:790  label: "Documentation"
  PAI/TOOLS/ActivityParser.ts:594-597  categoryNames map
    Display labels for human-readable section headers, not paths.

  PAI/TOOLS/ArchitectureSummaryGenerator.ts:27
    path.join(PAI_DIR, "DOCUMENTATION", "Memory", "MemorySystem.md")
    DOCUMENTATION children are intentionally mixed-case in upstream
    (Agents, Algorithm, Memory, Notifications, etc.). Path correct.

Co-existence: patches 0005 and 0008 both modify actions.ts but at
non-overlapping line ranges. Hunks generated via `diff -u` against
the post-0008 result/ tree to ensure line numbers match the
post-0001-0008 state at patch-application time.

Total: 4 files, 4 hunks, 4 line changes.
